&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Business, Finance, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 5 years’ experience in banking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven sales track record in generating deposit growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong business development skills with an entrepreneurial mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work and thrive in a high-growth, fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
